INSERT INTO `gun` VALUES (111011,'MP5',111010,10071,'The MP5 is a famous and effective weapon, with a reasonably fast fire rate, upon opening fire it can unload a great deal of suppressing fire. One MP5 is able to unload the killing effectiveness of a few guns put together, and often causes severe lacerations in its targets, making recovery difficult. The MP5\'s low recoil and high accuracy make it a reasonable comfortable experience when shooting. Add to this its reasonable price and easy operation making this a weapon that everyone in the wasteland can use, whether they\'re a man, woman, old or young. ','MP5是一款精度与射速俱佳的冲锋枪，装弹迅速，短时间内能打出恐怖的连射火力，不愧是反恐利器。','步枪',1,60,0,22,0,6,0,72,0,25,0,67,0,86,0,8.5,0,1.99,0,22,0,0,0),(112011,'TAR-21',112010,20001,'The TAR-21 is an unsupported rifle, it uses 5.56 diameter bullets, and packs a kick. TAR-21 is more reliable than the M4, it is reliable when firing and its recoil is lower than the M4. However, the gun\'s accuracy doesn\'t mean that you can just spray and hope to hit your target, but the probability of killing your target with an aimed shot is high. Traces of the TAR-21 can be found all over the wasteland, and is in the displays of many arms dealer\'s stores, there once was even two large arms dealers who ended up fighting over the TAR-21\'s naming rights.','TAR-21是一款无托结构步枪，有着狙击枪的精准度与高射速，且后座力很小，弹道稳定，适合中远距离作战。','步枪',1,83.1,0,14,0,5,0,70,0,32,0,77,0,61,0,8.4,0,2.09,0,14,0,0,0),(112021,'F2000',112020,20002,'The FN2000 was designed for battle in the wasteland, as sandstorms, acid rains and deep dark nights are regularly seen occurrences in the wasteland which make a lot of trouble for battling mercenaries. The FN2000 has a unique 1.6x optical scope which is designed to deal with these problems. Of course, the FN2000 is also fashionable, with a sleek design which gives it a futuristic look and feel. The Wanderer\'s describes the FN2000 as “A gun which has both power and aesthetic beauty in one, holding it while killing your enemies will make you look cool and will also increases your manliness by 5%!”','FN2000是一款紧凑型无托步枪，外形美观、太空感十足，精准度很高，且在酸雨、黄沙、暗夜等恶劣环境中威力不减。','步枪',1,79.3,0,8,0,4.6,0,76,0,30,0,81,0,58,0,8.6,0,2.06,0,8,0,0,0),(113011,'AK47',113010,10011,'The AK47 is one of the most popular guns in the world due to its reliability, cheap cost and reasonable power. It doesn\'t break, jam or overheat easily and is able to fire even in muddy or sandy environment. Most importantly, this gun is easy to use; even a child can use it, and they do!','AK47是一款既耐用又精准的气动式步枪，特点是快准狠，适合多种环境作战。','步枪',1,96,0,32,0,7,0,42,0,30,0,75,0,32,0,9.4,0,2,0,32,0,0,0),(113021,'M4A1',113020,20003,'The M4A1 is a gun which is very popular with mercenaries because of its long range and high fire rate. It has a short and exquisite appearance, with a compact structure, a mercenary can even hide it in their over coat without it being discovered by the enemy. But this gun is not to be underestimated, loads of mercenaries who didn\'t take note of this gun have had their head blown up in a quick second giving their life as testament to the chilling power of this weapon!','M4A1是一款导气式突击步枪，射击速度快，远射程射击杀伤力很大，且枪身紧凑轻便，深受佣兵喜爱。','步枪',1,83.1,0,10,0,5,0,72,0,30,0,80,0,55,0,9.6,0,2.01,0,10,0,0,0),(113031,'ACR',113030,20004,'The ACR was one of the best assault rifles once upon a time, it uses a gas operated system and a quick changing barrel and apparently has a modular desinged system, and completely blew away the audience when it was first revealed at a firearms exhibition. The famous \"Wanderer\'s Magazine\" once wrote: \"A fighter named Barnes once used an ACR to save a group of ten mercenaries, fighting off over one hundred beasts! After this event, the ACR\'s price rose drastically!','ACR曾是最好的突击步枪之一，采用快换式枪管和导气式系统，射程远、后座力小，适合远程作战。','步枪',1,88.6,0,18,0,4.6,0,68,0,30,0,79,0,44,0,9.4,0,1.8,0,18,0,0,0),(113041,'AUG',113040,20005,'In the old era, the AUG was an un supported assault rifle widely used by special forces and law enforcement organizations due to its great accuracy, reliability at firing and its unmodest lethality. In addition, the AUG is small at the front but big at the back and smooth and compact, giving it a great look, many warriors in the wasteland carry an AUG equipped with a bayonet, this model was famous in the City Of Doom for a time.','斯太尔AUG是一款5.56mm口径突击步枪，射击精准、发弹可靠，而且空枪只有3.61KG，轻便耐用，深受佣兵们喜爱。','步枪',1,88.8,0,10,0,4.6,0,66,0,32,0,78,0,64,0,9.4,0,2.31,0,10,0,0,0),(114011,'SCAR-S',114010,20006,'The SCAR is a vicious firearm, hence the name scar, but the SCAR-S is much more functional than the SCAR, its firing accuracy is very high along with being really reliable, even if the magazine gets mud or dirt in it, it\'s operation won\'t be affected at all. \"Wanderer\'s Magazine\" even describes the SCAR-S as the most pricless treasure left over from the old era, even kids nowadays know, that as long as you have a SCAR-S in your hand, the water source belongs to you!','SCAR-S是一款多口径突击步枪，精准射击能打出粉碎性伤害，且可根据作战距离调整打法，性价比非常高。','步枪',1,93,0,25,0,5,0,54,0,20,0,81,0,68,0,10.4,0,2.2,0,25,0,0,0),(121011,'M60',121010,10061,'This was a world famous, time honored gun brand since the apocalypse. Possessing a gas operated automatic mode, and with  the range of a heavy machine gun but with the flexibility of a light machine gun, soldiers can equip the machine gun with a tripod and put it on a car or an aircraft to mow down enemies or just carry it with their own hands. If you have a set of eight pack abs, then you really suit the M60, shouldering the M60 whilst wearing nothing but golden bullet belts on the upper half of your body, opening fire upon the beasts with a \"DAKA DAKA DAKA\", that\'d truly be an awesome sight.','M60通用机枪是一款勋章卓著的老牌机枪，射程较远，枪身紧凑、使用灵活，是威力强大的支援武器。','机枪',2,65,0,20,0,12,0,60,0,60,0,58,0,55,0,8.2,0,3.5,0,20,0,0,0),(122011,'RPD',122010,20007,'A gas operated machine gun known as \"The soviet type writer of death”with a simple yet crude structure. It fires 7.62mm bullets and packs a fierce punch, whilst also being pretty accurate making this a gun suitable for mid-range combat, if youy\'re sighted by it then it\'s the equivalent of being painted with the mark of death. The RPD is also really light and portable, mercenaries who are familiar with guns will notice that the RPD has a net weight of just 7.1km, and the whole gun only has 65 parts making this a very convenient gun to carry!','RPD是一款轻便的导气式轻机枪，弹量充沛且射击稳定，且携带方便，适合行进中的中远距离作战。','机枪',2,74.8,0,14,0,3.8,0,68,0,60,0,65,0,24,0,8.6,0,3.96,0,14,0,0,0),(123011,'M249',123010,10091,'The M249 is a pneumatic type machine gun which fires 5.56mm diameter bullets. It\'s a light gun which can easily be carried by one person and has a huge magazine capacity allowing prolonged firepower. In addition, the M249 can guarantee reliability even in extremely harsh conditions such as snow, salt water, high temperature and high humidity, making this gun extremely durable. A lone mercenary surrounded by a pack of beasts or zombies still has a hope of survival when wielding the M249!','一款5.56mm口径气动式轻机枪，它便于携带，且弹量充沛、火力持久，在恶劣环境下依然威力不减。','机枪',2,64,0,25,0,5,0,62,0,60,0,66,0,42,0,10.5,0,3.9,0,25,0,0,0),(124011,'Gatling',124010,10021,'A machine gun which can make even aliens tremble with fear. This gun has a really fast fire rate, whilst also being shockingly powerful, its 6 rotating barrels can fire off 6000 bullets within one minute unleashing a tempest of power capable of turning its target into a bee hive. But it\'s very rare to see mercenaries running around with a gatling gun on their back as it\'s too heavy, and it consumes ammo way too quickly making it necessary to carry long belts of ammo in order to keep the gun well-supplied.','一款手动型多管机枪，射速快、威力恐怖，6个枪管旋转发射，暴风骤雨的子弹足以把目标打成蜂窝。','机枪',2,42,0,28,0,5,0,82,0,75,0,50,0,24,0,9,0,4.24,0,28,0,0,0),(131011,'AWM',131010,20008,'The AWM is a manual firing sniper rifle used by military personel and civilians alike. Developed from a hunting rifle, it has been modified to be able to fire two different types of ammo: both 7.62mm and 8.6mm diameter bullets can be used. The rifle\'s power and range has also been massively improved, allowing this gun to be used for long range defense and support without any problems. In the wasteland, many mercenaries use the AWM to kill beasts, but will also occasionally use it to wipe out invading bands of soldiers.','AWM是一款多口径手动式狙击枪，射程远、精度高，在旧时代曾打出2745m的狙击距离，是最好的狙击枪之一。','狙击枪',3,267,0,20,0,20.6,0,10,0,10,0,100,0,0,0,22,0,3.2,0,20,0,0,0),(132011,'SVD',132010,20009,'Many young and new mercenaries looking to buy an SVD in the black market will accidentally purchase an AK47 and will only realize upon using the gun that these are in fact two very different guns. The SVD may look very similar to the AK47, they both even have really similar looking bolts and bayonet sockets, but the SVD uses a gas piston, making it much more accurate and giving it a much longer range than the AK47, remember, this is a sniper rifle!','SVD是一款远射程班组支援武器，子弹威力大，穿透力极强，且和AK47一样耐用、可靠。','狙击枪',3,186.9,0,18,0,21.1,0,25,0,10,0,100,0,0,0,20,0,3.08,0,18,0,0,0),(133011,'PSG-1',133010,10051,'The PSG-1 is an expensive semi-automatic sniper rifle. It has outstanding accuarcy, being able to fire 50 bullets through a hole 8cm in diameter from 300 meters away, making this a really accurate gun to use in the wasteland. Also, after equipping its built in silencer, it makes very little noise when firing. Therefore, in the wasteland this gun has been given the fear-inspiring name \"The yellow Cobra\", it can deliver a silent, deadly blow in an instant, but the price is also very costly, don\'t even think about buying it unless you have a few gold bars lying around!','PSG-1是一款7.62口径半自动狙击枪，射击精准度小于1角分，采用内置消声器使其噪音很小，能打出恐怖的无声伤害。','狙击枪',3,156,0,30,0,25,0,15,0,15,0,100,0,100,0,16,0,2.67,0,30,0,0,0),(134011,'Barret M82A1',134010,10041,'The M82A1 is one of the earliest anti-material guns, which uses 12.7mm diameter bullets. Its bullets can pack a great punch, and can punch through walls, destroy trucks and fighters. The military doesn\'t recommend using 12.7mm bullets to shoot people however, as the power of one shot is too much and will blast a person into pieces, which is simply just too cruel and will turn the battle ground into a gorefest. ','M82A1是世界级反器材枪械之一，采用12.7mm口径子弹，威力恐怖，且射程远、精度高，用来摧毁机车、墙壁效果显著。','狙击枪',3,202,0,40,0,30,0,10,0,10,0,100,0,100,0,16.4,0,3.64,0,40,0,0,0),(141011,'M1014',141010,20010,'M1014 is a gas-operated, semi-auto shotgun. It\'s extremely versatile and suitable for multiple battle environments due to its retractable buttstock, anti-corrosive matte parts, night vision goggle and laser designator. Lots of mercenary vanguards prefer carrying an M1014 for night walks and defense. What\'s more, M1014 can survive any harsh environments such as acid rains and snowstorms. Due to the above reasons, many mercenaries consider it their life partner.','一款导气式半自动散弹枪，采用哑光化铁制零件和可伸缩的枪托，携带方便、耐用可靠，且适合在夜间作战。','霰弹枪',4,160.9,0,62,0,23.8,0,33,0,7,0,4,0,0,0,7.5,0,2.1,0,62,0,0,0),(142011,'Striker',142010,20011,'The striker is a uniquely moulded semi-automatic shotgun, the body of the gun is short and finely made, and the bullet nest is round, making this gun an unforgettable sight. It\'s power is also not to be trifled at, each bullet has massive blast strength, and it is easy to quickly fire off rounds, continuously firing rounds \"DAKA　DAKA　DAKA\" turning a close range target into swiss cheese. However, experienced soldiers will notice that the Striker has a slow reload rate, meaning that unless you are in cover, it\'s probably best not to fire off all of your bullets in one go.','打击者是一款采用12发旋转弹巢式弹鼓供弹的半自动霰弹枪，速射方便，连续射击伤害恐怖，但换弹速度较慢。','霰弹枪',4,182.2,0,60.8,0,32.1,0,22,0,12,0,16,0,0,0,7.2,0,2.24,0,60.8,0,0,0),(143011,'Remington M870',143010,10031,'The M870 is a pump-action shotgun that is a household name. The power of its shots is great and it\'s reliable to operate, making it a lethal close-ranged weapon best used for self defense. The M870\'s price is also mid-ranged, even with beasts all over the world, and with hardware stores selling out of the M870, its price remains reasonable, thus is has become known across the wasteland as the \"Guard\'s Gun\".','M870是一款需手动填弹的泵动式散弹枪，威力恐怖，破坏力极大，是近战杀伤利器。','霰弹枪',4,142,0,35,0,20,0,16,0,7,0,10,0,100,0,6.2,0,2.64,0,35,0,0,0),(143021,'Jackhammer',143020,20012,'Jackhammer is an unsupported fully-automatic shotgun, which uses a unique revolving magazine, the body of the gun is short and finely made, making this gun an unforgettable sight. Jackhammer has a rapid fire function, making it able to fire off 240 shells in one minute. The fierce firepower of this weapon will stop close range targets from being able to dodge its fire, making this gun evidently effective when dealing with those larger beasts. Mercenaries wandering around the wasteland will sometime come across beast corpses riddled with holes and ripped to shreds, that is the fine work of Jackhammer!','汽锤是一款全自动独轮式散弹枪，射速极快，威力恐怖，近战能打出连续的粉碎性伤害。','霰弹枪',4,193.1,0,61.6,0,26.2,0,30,0,10,0,8,0,0,0,7.7,0,2.48,0,61.6,0,0,0),(144011,'AA12',144010,10081,'The Etcheson AA12 is a fully automatic shotgun with a high penetration degree. It has low recoil and has a great rapid fire function making this a very useful weapon. The AA12 is able to fire any number 12 sized diameter shells. Experienced soldiers will often use this gun to fire off smoke bombs, flares and other types of non-lethal bombs. If equipped with grenades, the power of this gun is even greater, with just one grenade this gun is able to blow up a sentry post, giving this gun the nickname \"The destroyer\"!','一款多用途全自动散弹枪，凡是12号口径子弹均可用它发射，且后座力小，精准度高，在近距离伏击战中表现霸道。','霰弹枪',4,71,0,36,0,14,0,32,0,20,0,25,0,100,0,6.5,0,2,0,36,0,0,0),(151011,'Silver Echo',151010,10101,'Silver Echo is Desert Eagle modified by Goro himself. It has fearsome power and very strong recoil. Few people other than Goro can use this special weapon.','MP5是一款精度与射速俱佳的冲锋枪，装弹迅速，短时间内能打出恐怖的连射火力，不愧是反恐利器。','手枪',1,35,0,28,0,25,0,90,0,24,0,80,0,80,0,7.5,0,1.76,0,28,0,0,0),(160001,'Mech\'s Weapon',124010,30001,'Mech\'s Weapon','一款手动型多管机枪，射速快、威力恐怖，6个枪管旋转发射，暴风骤雨的子弹足以把目标打成蜂窝。','',2,67,0,50,0,0,0,88,0,150,0,40,0,40,0,8,0,5,0,50,0,0,0),(160011,'Turret\'s Weapon',124010,30002,'Turret\'s Weapon','一款手动型多管机枪，射速快、威力恐怖，6个枪管旋转发射，暴风骤雨的子弹足以把目标打成蜂窝。','',2,40,0,50,0,0,0,50,0,9999,0,70,0,70,0,10,0,0,0,50,0,0,0),(161011,'Scorcher',161010,10111,'This weapon is created by FireKing from all kinds of scrapmetal that he could find in the wasteland, so it doesn\'t have a serial number, only the nickname: Scorcher. Nothing can withstand it\'s fiery power.','喷火器','喷火器',5,42,0,0,0,0,0,96,0,100,0,40,0,100,0,6.1,0,8,0,0,0,0,0),(171011,'Infinity Crossbow',171010,10121,'After years of wandering the wasteland Nasha created this powerful crossbow. Using ancient techniques she created a weapon that doesn\'t require projectile, it shoots energy itself.','电磁弩P-1','弩炮',6,102,0,28,0,23,0,25,0,18,0,90,0,90,0,17,0,2.3,0,28,0,0,0),(181011,'Electromagnetic (EM) Gun',181010,10131,'The EM gun is Capone\'s most skilled firearm. It was crafted by himself using the materials found in ruins and only he knows how to operate it. It requires plasma to provide the power needed for EM rounds, so Capone has to carry a giant plasma carrier along in combat. This weapon fits only him, a man of extraordinary fitness.','卡彭最擅长使用的电磁枪，这是他从遗迹中拼凑出来的特殊型号，只有卡彭才能使用。由于需要大量电浆来激发电磁射线，所以使用的时候需携带巨大的电浆桶。也只有卡彭这样体型巨大的人，才能随身携带这样笨重的武器。','电磁枪',7,39,0,23,0,13,0,100,0,10,0,1,0,100,0,5.5,0,1.5,0,0,0,0,0),(191011,'Grenade Launcher',191010,10141,'This is the MGL-140 Grenade Launcher. Patty is one of the few capable of using such highly destructive weapon well. She usually stays well behind the line of fire and lays waste to any opposing force.','这是MGL-140榴弹枪，很少有人能驾驭住这样威力巨大的武器，然而帕蒂却做到了。躲在后方尽情用榴弹枪对前线轰炸，是帕蒂最擅长的事情，这也成为许多人的噩梦。','榴弹炮',8,215,0,25,0,15,0,13,0,8,0,10,0,100,0,6,0,3,0,35,0,3,0.8);
